sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant VS as Istio VirtualService
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Agent as kserve-agent<br/>Queue Proxy
    participant Predictor as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    User->>Gateway: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Gateway->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
    Webhook-->>Gateway: Mutated InferenceService
    Gateway->>Controller: Watch CRD event
    Controller->>K8s: Create Knative Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS ServiceAccount
    Controller->>K8s: Create VirtualService<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS ServiceAccount
    K8s->>StorageInit: Init container starts
    StorageInit->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS AWS IAM
    S3-->>StorageInit: Model files
    StorageInit->>Agent: Model downloaded
    Agent->>Predictor: Start model server

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless + Istio)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>VS: Forward (TLS termination)<br/>mTLS STRICT
    VS->>Activator: Route request<br/>8012/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Activator->>Agent: Activate pod (scale from 0)<br/>8012/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Agent->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor-->>Agent: Prediction result
    Agent-->>Activator: Response
    Activator-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS TLS1.3

    Note over Client,Ensemble: Flow 3: InferenceGraph Multi-Model
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/ensemble:predict
    Gateway->>Router: Route to kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Router->>ModelA: Request to Model A<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    ModelA-->>Router: Response A
    Router->>ModelB: Request to Model B<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    ModelB-->>Router: Response B
    Router->>Ensemble: Combine results<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Ensemble-->>Router: Final result
    Router-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
